Finding the right talent doesn’t have to be a guessing game. TalentSnap AI is an advanced Generative AI-powered recruitment tool that evaluates resumes, job descriptions, and even external professional profiles — delivering precise fitment scores and intelligent role recommendations.

JobFit AI is a cutting-edge Generative AI-based recruitment utility that analyzes job descriptions and resumes to determine the perfect match — saving time, reducing manual effort, and improving hiring accuracy.



💡 Key Features:
✅ AI-Powered Resume Matching
Automatically evaluates resumes against job descriptions and scores how well the candidate fits the role.

✅ Skill Alignment Analysis
Breaks down how closely the resume matches primary and secondary skills outlined in the job description.

✅ External Profile Integration
Analyzes publicly available data from LinkedIn, GitHub, and more to enrich the candidate profile with verified skills and real-world project contributions.

✅ Fitment Score & Detailed Insights
Get a comprehensive fitment score, along with insights into experience, education, skill match, and role alignment.

✅ Smart Role Recommendations
If a candidate isn’t a good fit for the given role, TalentSnap AI doesn’t stop there. It intelligently suggests alternative roles that better match the candidate's background — saving time for both recruiters and candidates.
